[Student "S"]
{EAST could make a Help Suit Game Try in either \Ss or \Cs. 
But she doesn't need the \S help as much as she does in \Cs, so she chooses \Cs.

WEST doesn't have a strong hand but has excellent help in \Cs 
so he bids the game.}

