[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/advanced_forcing"]
[Student "S"]
{SOUTH bids 2\C as New Minor Forcing, hoping NORTH has three \Hs.

NORTH does not have three \Hs and he has no other bid to make that 
will describe his hand any better. He cannot bid Notrump again without a \C stopper. 
So NORTH rebids the 5-card \D suit.

SOUTH has nowhere to go, so passes.}

